As I am sure you are aware the legal system is in a unique and
unprecedented position. The Ontario Superior Court Chief Justice has
ensured that an accessible and effective family justice system continue to
function, and has outlined a guide to process, with variation among
jurisdictions, which builds on the Family Law Strategic Plan and the Child
Prioritization Initiative, the goal being, as I have said all along, to
reduce conflict which has the most damaging effects on children.

Yet your client continues to create conflict where none need exist, and I
have made multiple requests for alternative forms of resolution. But put
simply when your client was told no restrictions means no restrictions and
the case was closed, she took it upon herself to impose restrictions that
are more stringent than those outlined in the court orders. She has
interfered with and used control of the girls to interfere with my
relationship with my daughters, and their right to have a relationship with
me independent of interference. Your client has, numerous times, ensured
that I treated as the least important part of my daughter=E2=80=99s lives. =
