-          Can she provide evidence she is following provincial health
regulations?

-          Why is she restricting Facetime with the girls when they are
bored and cannot attend school? I am an educator, they enjoy talking to me,
yet she ends conversations for reasons including it=E2=80=99s time for a wa=
